        "System.Title": "Case Review - Determinations",
        "Microsoft.VSTS.Common.Priority": 2,
        "System.Description": "<p>Finalize a case by applying the appropriate determination outcome, generating and delivering all required notifications and documents, managing delivery exceptions, and completing the case in compliance with clinical, regulatory, and turnaround time requirements: </p><div style=\"margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:14px;\"><article tabindex=-1 dir=auto><div tabindex=-1><div><div dir=auto><ul><li>Apply Final Determination (Approval, Denial, Withdrawal, Out of Scope, PA Exempt) </li><li>Generate and Send Determination Notification Package </li><li>Complete and Close Case After Successful Notification Delivery </li> </ul> </div> </div><div> </div> </div></article><article tabindex=-1 dir=auto></article><br> </div><p> </p><br><br>"
